00:07:23.110 --> 00:07:26.100
come to the point of
saying, a giraffe's heart

00:07:26.100 --> 00:07:27.490
is going to be this big.

00:07:27.490 --> 00:07:30.060
You can go through a
different realm of logic built

00:07:30.060 --> 00:07:33.560
around evolutionary principles
