01:18:36.940 --> 01:18:38.350
These are the principles.

01:18:38.350 --> 01:18:40.930
And what people of this
school of evolutionary thought

01:18:40.930 --> 01:18:44.010
would say, armed with
these sorts of principles,

01:18:44.010 --> 01:18:47.200
you could now look at all
sorts of interesting domains

01:18:47.200 --> 01:18:49.980
of animal behavior
and understand

01:18:49.980 --> 01:18:53.200
