And you are trying to
figure out this strategy.

01:27:27.420 --> 01:27:30.760
So you are going to leave
and abandon your kids.

01:27:30.760 --> 01:27:34.080
In which species do
you see that behavior?

01:27:34.080 --> 01:27:35.070
The one on the right.

01:27:35.070 --> 01:27:37.980
The one on the right, because
